<div class="col-12 col-md-6">
    <h3 style="font-size:18px" class="pt-3 mt-3 mt-md-0" id="thingsToDoTitle">Pilgrimage</h3>
    <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:2" class="pt-1 text-justify m-0" id="thingsToDoDesc">
        Sikkim is a state in northeastern India. It borders Tibet in the north and northeast, Bhutan in the east, Nepal in the west, and West Bengal in the south. Sikkim is also located close to India&#39;s Siliguri Corridor near Bangladesh...
    </p>
    <div class="col-12 pl-0 py-3 py-md-0">
