                    <div class="travellerDiv card-body h-100">
                        <p style="font-weight:700">Restricted Area Permits</p>
                        <p class="card-text" style="font-size:14px">View essential permit information on the various restricted areas of Sikkim. </p>
                        <a href="/Public/TravellerEssentials/rap" class="btn btn-sm btn-link text-left text-decoration-none mt-2 p-0 w-100 font-weight-bold" style="color: #008CA1">
